re, son père, John Brancestre, avait 47 ans et sa mère, Margaret Mile, avait 31 ans. Elle a épousé Richard d'Anvers II en 1389, à Oxfordshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils. Elle est décédée environ 1395, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 37 ans, et a été enterrée à Oxfordshire, Angleterre."},"de":{"about 1360–about 1395":"um 1360–um 1395","1348–1391":"1348–1391","1348–Male":"1348–Verstorben","1352–Male":"1352–Verstorben","1359–1395":"1359–1395","1360–1395":"1360–1395","1330–1409":"1330–1409","1382–1448":"1382–1448","1315–1392":"1315–1392","1330–1392":"1330–1392","about 1360":"um 1360","1330":"1330","1352":"1352","1395":"1395","1382":"1382","1360":"1360","1392":"1392","1391":"1391","1448":"1448","1315":"1315","1359":"1359","1348":"1348","Bef 1392":"vor 1392","1389":"1389","1409":"1409","about 1395":"um 1395","Colthorpe, Oxfordshire, England":"Colthorpe, Oxfordshire, England","Cropredy Church, Oxfordshire, England":"Oxfordshire, England","Banbury, Oxfordshire, England":"Banbury, Oxfordshire, England","Oxfordshire, England":"Oxfordshire, England, United Kingdom","Ipswell, Oxfordshire, England":"Oxfordshire, England","Doncaster, Yorkshire, England":"Doncaster, Yorkshire, England","lifeSummary":"Als Agnes Brancestre um 1360 in Oxfordshire, England geboren wurde, war ihr Vater John Brancestre 47 und ihre Mutter Margaret Mile 31. Sie hat 1389 in Oxfordshire, England, United Kingdom Richard d'Anvers II geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Sohn. Sie starb um 1395 im Alter von 37 Jahren in ihrem Geburtsort und wurde in Oxfordshire, England begraben."},"ht":{"about 1360–about 1395":"about 1360–about 1395","1348–1391":"1348–1391","1348–Male":"1348–Desede","1352–Male":"1352–Desede","1359–1395":"1359–1395","1360–1395":"1360–1395","1330–1409":"1330–1409","1382–1448":"1382–1448","1315–1392":"1315–1392","1330–1392":"1330–1392","about 1360":"about 1360","1330":"1330","1352":"1352","1395":"1395","1382":"1382","1360":"1360","1392":"1392","1391":"1391","1448":"1448"